            "content": "<p>Your participation in this study is entirely voluntary, and you have the right to withdraw at any time without penalty or negative consequences. If you choose to withdraw, any data collected from you will be deleted and not included in the final analysis. <br>The purpose of this study is to assess the perception of different versions of a virtual character. You will be asked to watch 18 videos of a virtual character and answer questions about your perception of their behavior. Finally, we will ask for some demographic information to ensure unbiased demographic representation. <br> This study will take approximately 15 minutes to complete and will be rewarded 4.45$. The data collected in this study will be used for research purposes only. <br> If you have any questions, concerns, or feedback related to this study, please feel free to contact Lucie Galland at lucie.galland@lislab.fr. <br><br> Click Next to consent </p>"

